OL,3,CLiverpool goalkeeper fined for using
OL,4,Cphone on motorway
OL,6,FLiverpool FC goalkeeper Giorgi
OL,7,FMamardashvili was caught by police
OL,8,Fwatching a video on his phone while
OL,9,Fdriving along the motorway, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FThe footballer was pulled over on the
OL,13,FM6 and put into the back of a police
OL,14,Fcar after being spotting holding his
OL,15,Fphone near to the steering wheel of
OL,16,Fhis Audi.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
