PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779883867
OL,3,CLiverpool goalkeeper fined for using
OL,4,Cphone on motorway
OL,6,FThe 25-year-old Georgian
OL,7,Finternational, who signed for the Reds
OL,8,Fin 2025, has now been convicted of
OL,9,Fusing a handheld mobile phone while
OL,10,Fdriving a motor vehicle on a road.
OL,12,Fhe was sentenced at Warrington
OL,13,FCombined Court to a #440 fine,
OL,14,Freceived six penalty points on his
OL,15,Flicence, and was also ordered to pay
OL,16,F#120 costs and a #176 victim surcharge.
OL,18,FCheshire Police said Mamardashvili had
OL,19,Fbeen caught out at around 3:45pm on 27
OL,20,FJanuary, on the southbound carriageway
OL,21,Fof the M6 between Junctions 23 and 21.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779883867
OL,3,CLiverpool goalkeeper fined for using
OL,4,Cphone on motorway
OL,6,FThe court was told Mamardashvili gave
OL,7,Fhis name and identified himself with a
OL,8,FGeorgian driving licence.
OL,10,FFootage of the footballer's police
OL,11,Fstop was also captured on the
OL,12,Fofficer's bodyworn video, the court
OL,13,Fwas told.
OL,15,FMamardashvili has made 20 appearances
OL,16,Fthis season for Liverpool, recording
OL,17,Fthree clean sheets as he filled in for
OL,18,Fthe injured first-choice keeper
OL,19,FAlisson.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
