FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779883867
OL,3,CLiverpool goalkeeper fined for using
OL,4,Cphone on motorway
OL,6,FHe did not respond to the police
OL,7,Fprosecution notice, and his case was
OL,8,Fdealt with in a private hearing of the
OL,9,FSingle Justice Procedure.
OL,11,FNo plea was entered, and Mamardashvili
OL,12,Fwas found guilty on the strength of
OL,13,Fthe written police evidence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
